---
title: Sticky Sweet-Soy Beef Rump Tacos with Asian Slaw & Sriracha Mayo
description: Sometimes it can be tricky to find new ways to jazz up tacos but not tonight - onion chutney on beef is taking out the guesswork and creating new inspiration for your taco night. We also threw a herby mayo into the slaw for a bit of fun.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/659486f5b6e284551035ad04-e4ca6b73.jpeg
